sql: SELECT dob,COUNT(*) AS Total FROM locations WHERE ST_Within(point_h3,toSphericalGeography(ST_GeomFromText('POLYGON((-105.080 38.980, -105.020 38.980, -105.020 38.920, -105.080 38.920, -105.080 38.980))'))) IS True OR ST_Within(point_h3,toSphericalGeography(ST_GeomFromText('POLYGON((-105.110 38.960, -105.050 38.960, -105.050 38.900, -105.110 38.900, -105.110 38.960))'))) IS True GROUP BY dob ORDER BY Total DESC;
